data.description: 3 Bedrooms and Over 1,870 Sq Foot!!!  Looking for a lot of house for a good price?  Well you found it!  This home has so many awesome features including my favorite the 4 season room with windows that surround you and 2 sky lights for more natural lighting*French doors leading to a huge dining area with a gas fireplace*3 large bedrooms with huge closets, wood flooring*Primary bedroom upstairs has its own half bath, plenty of built in dressers for extra storage and more closets*Wood molding and doors through out*New Furnace & A/C in 2022***Electrical panel has just been updated***Attached garage, fenced in yard, huge corner lot, great location, close to shopping, schools and freeway* BATAVI-all measurements are approx. Exclude: kitchen island & trampoline
